                    (click)='open(modalScrollable, {scrollable: true})'
                ) Launch Scrollable Modal

            .sbp-preview-code
                sbpro-code-sample(
                    [codeSamples]='codeSamplesModalScroll',
                )

            .sbp-preview-text.
                Use the <code>&#123;scrollable: true&#125;</code> NgbModalOptions to make longer modal content scroll
                within the modal body if the contents is longer than the viewport height.


